OL,6,FCough and cold medicines which contain
OL,7,Fpholcodine are being withdrawn over
OL,8,Fsafety concerns.
OL,10,FThe medicines are being withdrawn
OL,11,Ffollowing a review which found the
OL,12,Frisks of a very rare allergic reaction
OL,13,Flinked to pholcodine outweighed the
OL,14,Fhealth benefits of the drug.
OL,16,FThe allergic reaction has been
OL,17,Fdescribed as a "very rare event" of
OL,18,Fanaphylaxis in patients who receive
OL,19,Fgeneral anaesthesia involving muscle
OL,20,Frelaxants (neuromuscular blocking
OL,21,Fagents.)
OL,3,CSome cough and cold medicines withdrawn
OL,4,Cfrom UK sale over safety concerns
